extends layout

block content
  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .mx-card.p-5.mb-5
      .row.align-items-center.gy-4
        .col-lg-7
          span.mx-section-title.text-uppercase.fw-semibold About the platform
          h1.display-5.fw-bold.mt-3 MoviezExpressRentals
          p.lead.text-muted.mt-3 An enterprise-ready movie rental experience that blends curated entertainment with powerful staff workflows and solid operational tooling.
        .col-lg-5
          .d-flex.flex-column.gap-3
            .d-flex.align-items-center.gap-3
              span.rounded-circle.bg-light.bg-opacity-10.d-inline-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center(style='width: 52px; height: 52px;')
                i.fas.fa-clapperboard.text-danger
              div
                h5.fw-semibold.mb-1 Cinematic Library
                p.text-muted.mb-0 Thousands of titles across genres, eras, and formats.
            .d-flex.align-items-center.gap-3
              span.rounded-circle.bg-light.bg-opacity-10.d-inline-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center(style='width: 52px; height: 52px;')
                i.fas.fa-users-gear.text-warning
              div
                h5.fw-semibold.mb-1 Team Collaboration
                p.text-muted.mb-0 Purpose-built dashboards for customers, staff, managers, and admins.
            .d-flex.align-items-center.gap-3
              span.rounded-circle.bg-light.bg-opacity-10.d-inline-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center(style='width: 52px; height: 52px;')
                i.fas.fa-shield-halved.text-info
              div
                h5.fw-semibold.mb-1 Secure Operations
                p.text-muted.mb-0 Role-based access, audit trails, and hardened data workflows.

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .row.g-4
      each item in featureItems
        .col-md-4
          .mx-card.h-100.p-4.shadow-hover
            span.rounded-circle.bg-light.bg-opacity-10.d-inline-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.mb-4(style='width: 56px; height: 56px;')
              i.fas.fa-lg.text-danger(class=item.icon)
            h4.fw-semibold=item.title
            p.text-muted.mb-0=item.text

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .mx-card.p-5
      .row.g-4
        .col-lg-6
          h2.h4.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-cookie-bite.me-3.text-warning
            | Privacy & Cookies
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-3
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.mt-1
              span
                strong Session cookies: 
                | express-session maintains authentication contexts securely.
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.mt-1
              span
                strong Secure sessions: 
                | HTTP-only cookies with proper expiration and domain settings.
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-check-circle.text-success.mt-1
              span
                strong No third-party tracking: 
                | We avoid analytics pixels or advertising scripts.
        .col-lg-6
          h2.h4.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-user-shield.me-3.text-info
            | Data Protection
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-3
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-lock.text-info.mt-1
              span
                strong Password security: 
                | BCrypt hashing with adaptive salt rounds protects credentials.
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-database.text-info.mt-1
              span
                strong MySQL storage: 
                | Extended Sakila schema with parameterized queries prevents SQL injection.
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-eye-slash.text-info.mt-1
              span
                strong Privacy first: 
                | No data sharing outside operational requirements.
            li.d-flex.gap-3
              i.fas.fa-shield-halved.text-info.mt-1
              span
                strong Role-based access: 
                | Middleware-enforced permissions for customer, staff, manager, and admin roles.

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .row.g-4
      .col-xl-4
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          span.mx-section-title.text-uppercase.fw-semibold.mb-3 Platform stack
          h3.h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-layer-group.me-3.text-danger
            | Core Technologies
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li
              strong Node.js & Express.js:
              |  RESTful API with layered architecture (Controller → Service → DAO).
            li
              strong Pug Templates:
              |  Server-side rendering with Bootstrap 5 responsive components.
            li
              strong MySQL2:
              |  Database driver with connection pooling and parameterized queries.
            li
              strong BCrypt:
              |  Secure password hashing with adaptive salt rounds.
      .col-xl-4
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          span.mx-section-title.text-uppercase.fw-semibold.mb-3 Open Source Libraries
          h3.h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-code-branch.me-3.text-warning
            | Dependencies
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li
              strong Authentication:
              |  express-session, connect-flash, cookie-parser for secure user sessions.
            li
              strong Logging:
              |  Winston with file rotation and structured logging levels.
            li
              strong Environment:
              |  dotenv for configuration management and environment variables.
            li
              strong Utilities:
              |  serve-favicon, http-errors, debug for enhanced development experience.
      .col-xl-4
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          span.mx-section-title.text-uppercase.fw-semibold.mb-3 Development Tools
          h3.h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-tools.me-3.text-info
            | Quality & Testing
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li
              strong Cypress Testing:
              |  End-to-end testing suite covering authentication, rentals, and admin workflows.
            li
              strong Code Quality:
              |  Prettier for consistent formatting and code style standards.
            li
              strong CI/CD Pipeline:
              |  GitHub Actions with automated testing using start-server-and-test.
            li
              strong Development:
              |  Callback-only async pattern following Node.js conventions.

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    h2.h3.fw-semibold.mb-4 User stories
    .row.g-4
      .col-lg-6
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          span.badge.mx-pill.mx-pill-soft.text-uppercase.fw-semibold.mb-3 Customer
          h4.fw-semibold.mb-3 "As a customer, I want to discover and rent movies so that I can enjoy curated entertainment at home."
          h5.text-muted.small.text-uppercase.mb-3 Acceptance criteria
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li - Search by title, category, rating, or staff recommendations.
            li - Add and manage rentals with clear due dates and pricing.
            li - Monitor spending history, loyalty offers, and membership status.
            li - Receive alerts for expiring rentals or new releases.
      .col-lg-6
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          span.badge.mx-pill.mx-pill-soft.text-uppercase.fw-semibold.mb-3 Staff
          h4.fw-semibold.mb-3 "As a staff member, I want to curate offers and track selections so that customers discover hidden gems."
          h5.text-muted.small.text-uppercase.mb-3 Acceptance criteria
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li - Approve or retire promotional film offers in one click.
            li - Maintain watchlists and featured rows for homepage placement.
            li - Review customer interest and inventory levels before recommending titles.
            li - Collaborate with managers on seasonal programming.
            li - Access role-specific dashboards with performance metrics.
      .col-lg-6
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          span.badge.mx-pill.mx-pill-soft.text-uppercase.fw-semibold.mb-3 Admin
          h4.fw-semibold.mb-3 "As an administrator, I want governance over users, films, and security so that the platform remains compliant."
          h5.text-muted.small.text-uppercase.mb-3 Acceptance criteria
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li - provide and deactivate staff accounts with company email validation and role assignments.
            li - Manage film catalog metadata, availability, pricing, and procurement notes.
            li - delete and update user accounts with audit history.
            li - create promotional offers with custom discount percentages and durations, for the staff to approve.
            li - add and remove movie stocks, respecting current rentals.

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .mx-card.p-5
      h2.h3.fw-semibold.mb-4 Technical pillars
      .row.g-4
        .col-md-4
          .mx-card.h-100.p-4
            h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
              i.fas.fa-shield-halved.me-2.text-danger
              | Security & Authentication
            ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
              li Role-based access control with middleware protection on all routes.
              li BCrypt password hashing with secure session management.
              li Parameterized SQL queries preventing injection attacks.
              li Environment-based configuration with secure defaults.
        .col-md-4
          .mx-card.h-100.p-4
            h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
              i.fas.fa-chart-simple.me-2.text-warning
              | Analytics & Reporting
            ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
              li Staff performance reports with rental and revenue metrics.
              li Customer spending analysis with period-based breakdowns.
              li Film inventory management with availability tracking.
              li Custom dashboard views for different user roles.
        .col-md-4
          .mx-card.h-100.p-4
            h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
              i.fas.fa-sparkles.me-2.text-info
              | Experience Design
            ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
              li Bootstrap 5 theming for consistent responsive layouts.
              li FontAwesome iconography drives recognizable actions.
              li Smooth hover states and subtle motion cues delight users.
              li Accessibility-first semantics and keyboard-friendly flows.

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .row.g-4
      .col-lg-6
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          h3.h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-clipboard-list-check.me-3.text-success
            | Development Standards
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li Layered architecture with strict separation of concerns (Controller → Service → DAO).
            li Callback-only async pattern following Node.js error-first conventions.
            li Comprehensive input validation and sanitization at service layer.
            li Cypress end-to-end test coverage for authentication, rentals, and admin workflows.
      .col-lg-6
        .mx-card.h-100.p-4
          h3.h5.fw-semibold.mb-3
            i.fas.fa-graduation-cap.me-3.text-info
            | Academic Project
          ul.list-unstyled.vstack.gap-2.text-muted
            li Educational demonstration of enterprise-level web application development.
            li Comprehensive feature set covering multiple user roles and workflows.
            li Real-world technologies and best practices for learning purposes.
            li GitHub repository with complete documentation and setup instructions.

  section.mx-section.pt-0
    .mx-card.p-5.text-center.shadow-hover
      h2.h3.fw-semibold.mb-3 Ready to explore more?
      p.lead.text-muted.mb-4 Dive into the full catalog, manage rentals, or collaborate with your team all inside MoviezExpressRentals.
      .d-flex.justify-content-center.flex-wrap.gap-3
        a.btn.btn-accent.btn-lg.px-4.rounded-pill(href='/films')
          i.fas.fa-film.me-2
          | Browse films
        a.btn.btn-outline-accent.btn-lg.px-4.rounded-pill(href='/reports')
          i.fas.fa-chart-pie.me-2
          | View analytics
